name: Galaga 3
description:
Galaga 3 was produced by Namco in 1984.

Namco released 303 different machines in our database under this trade name, starting in 1978.

Other machines made by Namco during the time period Galaga 3 was produced include Gaplus, Super Xevious, Dragon Buster, Shoot Away, Tower Of Druaga, The, Libble Rabble, Pac-Man & Chomp Chomp, Mappy, Phozon, and Pac & Pal.

Another shooting game in which you can capture the enemies and make them work with you if you hit the queen ship when it dives. Not widely known because released during video game crash.
